Webex App | Merge two phone calls
When you're on a phone call and you receive an incoming phone call in Webex App, you can merge the two phone calls into one and have everyone in the same phone call.
Desktop
Mobile
1
When you have an active phone call and you receive another phone call, select Hold and Answer Call.
Your active phone call is put on hold and the incoming call is answered.
2
Select More , select Merge, and then choose the phone call to merge.
The original call is resumed and merged with the incoming call. You can view the participants in the phone call by selecting .